title: Punisher v7 (01 - 21 & Annual) (complete) (- Nem -)
description:
The Punisher Volume 7

The series is somewhat of a continuation of Frank's adventures in Punisher War Journal Vol.2 that stopped a month before this series started. Written by Rick Remender, following the Punisher in the wake of Dark Reign and his struggles with Norman Osborn. The series took a turn to the controversial with the "Franken-Castle" storyline. Beginning with issue #17, the series changes its title to Franken-Castle.

At the same time this series started The Punisher Vol.6 (that was part of the MAX comics imprint and does not feature the 616 reality or "Main Marvel Universe" Punisher) changed it's name to Punisher: Frank Castle to avoid confusion with this title.
